NGUVA YE UCHAPUPU

0:01:00.260,0:01:05.560
Zita rangu ndi Joshua Sunday Oladele.

0:01:05.560,0:01:12.880
Mudzimai ari pedyo neni ndiye mudzimai wangu akanaka.

0:01:12.880,0:01:20.700
Chakandiudza pa SCOAN chaiva kutyoka kwe pfupa repachidya

0:01:20.700,0:01:24.080
Zvakaitika muna 2014.

0:01:24.080,0:01:31.260
Kune kubwinya kwa Mwari, ndakauya pano muna 2015, ndakasangana nomunhu wa Mwari akaisa maoko pamusoro pangu akandinyengeterera.

0:01:31.260,0:01:38.680
Ndakasimuka uye kubvira ipapo, ndakatanga kufamba.

0:01:38.680,0:01:44.440
Ndisati ndauya ku SCOAN, ndakanga ndaedza nzvimbo dzakawanda.

0:01:44.440,0:01:49.320
Zuva rekutanga chairo apo njodzi yacho yakaitika, ndakaendeswa kuchipatara.

0:01:49.320,0:01:52.120
Ndakaenda ku n'anga ndikagara pamba payo kwemwedzi mitatu.

0:01:52.120,0:01:59.700
Mushure memwedzi mitatu, akandiudza kuti ndiende kundotenga madondoro kuti ndishandise pakufamba. Zvaizondinakira

0:01:59.700,0:02:01.780
Ndakatenga madondoro, ndichibva ndabva panzvimbo iyoyo.

0:02:01.780,0:02:07.000
Pandakasvika kumba, ndakaona kuti pfupa rakanga risina kubatana.

0:02:07.000,0:02:10.860
Saka ndakaenda kune imwe na'nga

0:02:10.860,0:02:13.480
Zvechokwadi, ndakaedza n'anga dzakawanda.

0:02:13.480,0:02:16.660
Mhedzisiro yacho, takaona kuti mamiriro aya akanga asiri ega.

0:02:16.660,0:02:20.180
Takatanga kufamba kubva kuchechi imwe kuenda kune imwe tichitsvaga kununurwa.

0:02:20.180,0:02:22.400
Kunyange zvakadaro, pakanga pasina mhinduro.

0:02:22.400,0:02:25.580
Pekupedzisira Mwari akanditungamirira ku SCOAN.

0:02:25.580,0:02:27.580
Ndakawana mukana wekusangana nomunhu wa Mwari.

0:02:27.580,0:02:33.520
Pakarepo paakandibata, ndakasimuka ndikafamba.

0:02:33.520,0:02:35.960
Kare, ndakanga ndisingagoni kuenda kunzvimbo yangu yekushanda

0:02:35.960,0:02:38.560
Ndakatorasikirwa ne basa rangu panguva yandakanga ndine dambudziko

0:02:38.560,0:02:42.620
nokuti njodzi yacho haina kuitika munguva yekushanda,

0:02:42.620,0:02:47.940
Apo vaitarisira kuti ndidzoke kubasa nenguva uye vakaona kuti handaikwanisa kudzokera kubasa rangu,

0:02:47.940,0:02:52.420
ivo vakatumira muhoro wangu.

0:02:52.420,0:02:56.800
Zvakanga zvakaoma zvikuru kuwana chekudya nekuti ndini ndaive muriritiri wemhuri.

0:02:56.800,0:02:59.120
Handaikwanisa kuenda kunoshanda.

0:02:59.120,0:03:02.440
Mudzimai wangu ndiye aindichengeta.

0:03:02.440,0:03:08.300
Handaikwanisa kugeza kana kuenda kuchimbudzi ndoga.

0:03:08.300,0:03:10.960
Chaizvoizvo, zvakanga zvakaoma zvikuru.

0:03:10.960,0:03:15.460
Asi mushure memunyengetero wemu Porofita T.B. Joshua, iwe wakakwanisa kuita zvinhu zvose zvawaive usingagoni kuita ipapo.

0:03:15.460,0:03:22.720
Mushure memunyengetero wemu Porofita T.B. Joshua, kekutanga, ndakasimuka ndikafamba ndisina madondoro.

0:03:22.720,0:03:26.480
Zvakanaka, pane chimwe chinhu chatinoda kukubvunza.

0:03:26.480,0:03:31.780
Chii chaive chichiitika kwauri apo munhu wa Mwari aikunamatira nokuti takaona gumbo rako richifamba famba?

0:03:31.780,0:03:35.120
Tiudze - wakanga uchinzwa sei ipapo apo munhu wa Mwari aikunamatira

0:03:35.120,0:03:40.140
Apo munhu wa Mwari akarova rova gumbo rangu, ndakanzwa kupisa.

0:03:40.140,0:03:44.040
Paakandiudza kuti ndisimuke, ndakanzwa sokuti chimwe chinhu chakadonhera pasi kubva mugumbo rangu.

0:03:44.040,0:03:51.720
Ndakanzwa kunge mhete, chimwe chinhu - ndakanzwa kuti chimwe chinhu chakadonha kubva pagumbo rangu.

0:03:51.720,0:03:53.340
Akandiudza kuti ndifambe.

0:03:53.340,0:03:54.760
Ndipo pandakatanga kufamba.

0:03:54.760,0:04:00.840
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu wezvishamiso!

0:04:00.840,0:04:04.780
Neizvo Tenzi akaita muupenyu hwako, kukusunungura kubva pane dambudziko iroro,

0:04:04.780,0:04:09.260
Nderipi shoko raunaro rekupa mazano kune vanhu varikukuteera pasi pose?

0:04:09.260,0:04:17.400
Shoko rangu rekuyambira kune vatariri pasi pose uye munhu wose arikundiona izvozvi ndeye kuti

0:04:17.400,0:04:20.960
Tinofanira kuva nokutenda muna Mwari.

0:04:20.960,0:04:26.460
Sezvinogara zvichaturwa nemunhu wa Mwari kuti, kana iwe une dambudziko, unofanira kuuya kuna Mwari,

0:04:26.460,0:04:28.980
usatiza kubva kuna Mwari.

0:04:28.980,0:04:38.140
Kwandiri, kwaiva apo pandakauya ku SCOAN apo ndakagamuchira kuporeswa kwangu pasina kubhadhara peni kana naira.

0:04:38.140,0:04:44.060
Kune dzimwe nzvimbo dzandakamboenda, ndakapedza mari yakawanda - vamwe vaindibhadharisa 50,000 naira,

0:04:44.060,0:04:49.020
pa nzvimbo yekutanga vakandibhadharisa 80,000 naira, yechipiri 50,000 naira, vamwe 40 000 naira.

0:04:49.020,0:04:54.600
Saka izvo zvauri kutitaurira ndezvokuti pawakasvika pa SCOAN, uye Mwari akashandisa mu Profita T.B. Joshua

0:04:54.600,0:04:59.160
kuti akunamatire muzita ra Jesu Kristu iwe ukasunungurwa, hapana mari yaakatora kubva kwauri?

0:04:59.160,0:05:02.540
Hapana mari yakatorwa kubva kwandiri. Zvakanga zviri zve mahara.

0:05:02.540,0:05:05.940
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Ishe Jesu Kristu.

0:05:05.940,0:05:07.440
Ngatinzwei kubva kumudzimai wako.

0:05:07.440,0:05:10.920
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:05:10.920,0:05:17.780
Zita rangu ndi Temitope Oladele. Murume akamira pedyo neni ndiye murume wangu.

0:05:17.780,0:05:23.620
Ndinotenda Mwari nhasi nokuti ndiri kufara kwazvo.

0:05:23.620,0:05:31.220
Apo takasvika pano makore maviri apfuura tikasangana nomu Porofita T.B. Joshua pano,

0:05:31.220,0:05:35.700
akanyengeterera murume wangu uye murume wangu achibva afamba pakarepo.

0:05:35.700,0:05:37.320
Ndiri kufara kwazvo.

0:05:37.320,0:05:41.680
Zvaisava nyore nokuti ndini ndega ndaimubatsira

0:05:41.680,0:05:48.280
uye kuchengeta vana pamwe nekupa zvokudya. Ndini ndakanga ndichiita zvose.

0:05:48.280,0:05:53.440
Asi mushure memunyengetero akasunungurwa, anogona kuita zvose ega. - Ehe.

0:05:53.440,0:05:55.560
Uye iwe unofara kwazvo pamusoro pazvo. - Ehe.

0:05:55.560,0:05:58.160
Tinotenda Mwari Wemasimbaose pane izvo Tenzi vakaita muupenyu hwako.

0:05:58.160,0:06:02.340
Ungagone here kuekesaiza muviri wako uratidze vanhu izvo Tenzi vakakuitirai -

0:06:02.340,0:06:05.000
zvinhu izvo wakanga usingagoni kuita ipapo.

0:06:05.000,0:06:07.560
Ipapo ndakange ndisingagoni kumira nekufamba sezvizvi.

0:06:07.560,0:06:16.220
Asi ikozvino, ini ndave kugona kumira negumbo iri, ndinokwanisa kufamba ne kumhanya.

0:06:16.220,0:06:18.040
Kukudzwa ngakuve kuna Mwari wekumusoro soro.

